OL,6,FThe Executive have agreed to release
OL,7,F#688 million to settle outstanding pay
OL,8,Fawards for public sector workers.
OL,10,FIndividual departments have each been
OL,11,Fgiven an allocation and negotiation
OL,12,Fbetween trade unions and employers can
OL,13,Fnow progress.
OL,15,FThis comes after workers from various
OL,16,Fsectors engaged in major strike action
OL,17,Fover recent months.
