OL,6,FMultiple unions have taken to the
OL,7,Fpicket lines to protest over the
OL,8,Ffailure to make pay awards during
OL,9,FStormont's powersharing impasse.
OL,11,FThe Executive met for the first time
OL,12,Fon Thursday after powersharing was
OL,13,Frestored earlier this month.
OL,15,FStormont's restoration opened the way
OL,16,Ffor a resolution to the disputes and
OL,17,Fmany unions have suspended plans for
OL,18,Ffurther industrial action pending the
OL,19,Foutcome of pay talks with Stormont
OL,20,Fdepartments.
