OL,6,FThe money was included in the UK
OL,7,FGovernment's #3.3 million package to
OL,8,Fsupport the restoration of
OL,9,Fpowersharing at Stormont.
OL,11,FHowever, the funds allocated for
OL,12,Faddressing the delayed pay awards for
OL,13,Fpublic sector workers only covers the
OL,14,Fcurrent financial year.
OL,16,FIt will be up the Executives'
OL,17,Fresponsibility to budget for
OL,18,Fsustaining pay levels going forward.
