OL,6,FThe allocation of the money to
OL,7,Fdepartments was agreed following a
OL,8,Fproposal by Finance Minister Caoimhe
OL,9,FArchibald.
OL,11,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill and
OL,12,Fdeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,13,FPengelly along with Ms Archibald spoke
OL,14,Fto reporters at Stormont Castle after
OL,15,Fthe meeting.
OL,17,F"We were determined to make some early
OL,18,Fdecision and I'm glad that we've been
OL,19,Fable to do that," Ms O'Neill said.
