OL,6,F"We had said that whenever we returned
OL,7,Fas an Executive that we would work
OL,8,Ftowards making sure that workers had
OL,9,Ffair pay.
OL,11,F"So, I'm delighted to say that today
OL,12,Fthe Executive, on the recommendation
OL,13,Fof the Finance Minister, has decided
OL,14,Fto allocate over #685 million which
OL,15,Fwill allow conversations now to
OL,16,Fcommence between employers and trade
OL,17,Funions in relation to public sector
OL,18,Fpay."
