OL,6,FMs O'Neill said ministers were united
OL,7,Fin pushing for more money for Northern
OL,8,FIreland.
OL,10,F"I know we are united as an Executive
OL,11,Fin terms of the challenges that we
OL,12,Fhave ahead of us but also the need to
OL,13,Fensure that we have a properly funded
OL,14,Fpublic service model," she said.
OL,16,FMs Little-Pengelly added: "The people
OL,17,Fof Northern Ireland deserve public
OL,18,Fservices that work for them.
