OL,6,F"We know that there's big challenges
OL,7,Fwithin our public services but, of
OL,8,Fcourse, we must recognise that the
OL,9,Fpeople who deliver those public
OL,10,Fservices, our public servants, deserve
OL,11,Ffair pay.
OL,13,F"And that's why this step today of the
OL,14,Fallocation of #685 million for the
OL,15,Fpurposes of negotiation, and hopefully
OL,16,Fquick settlement, is a really welcome
OL,17,Fone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
