OL,6,F"We do want to get these issues
OL,7,Fresolved because our public sector
OL,8,Fworkers have deserved that fair pay,
OL,9,Fbut they have deserved that before
OL,10,Fthis point.
OL,12,F"So we do hope that we're able to
OL,13,Fresolve that and I welcome the fact
OL,14,Fthat the #3.3 billion package secured
OL,15,Fwith the UK Government has been able
OL,16,Fto enable this announcement today in
OL,17,Fterms of the settlement for this year."
OL,19,FMs Archibald said she was "delighted"
OL,20,Fto secure Executive approval for the
OL,21,Fallocation.
