OL,6,F"This is a really good day for our
OL,7,Fpublic sector workers who've had to
OL,8,Fwait too long for their pay award, for
OL,9,Four health care workers, our teachers,
OL,10,Four police, our civil servants, and it
OL,11,Fwill enable negotiations to begin
OL,12,Fimmediately with trade unions," she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"And I want to see those conclude as
OL,16,Fquickly as possible to ensure that
OL,17,Fworkers are getting a fair pay award
OL,18,Fand that they're actually seeing that
OL,19,Fmoney in their pay packets as quickly
OL,20,Fas possible.
